{"tid":1932128,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派提削特首辦及警隊開支　立法會明天繼續審議","createTime":"2020-03-18T14:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T12:56:10.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f818aa4e842a18c3b6641768422427c99debb49","tid":1932128,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>民主派議員質疑「魔鬼在細節」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n立法會今日審議由政府提出涉及約2159億元的臨時撥款決議案，有民主派議員質疑「魔鬼在細節」，提出修訂削減特首辦和警隊的開支。立法會暫停會議，明早繼續審議議案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/02/20200214_PO_%E8%AC%9D%E5%81%89%E9%8A%931.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F02%2F20200214_PO_%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%258A%25931.jpg&h=f183780a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝偉銓。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n監警會副主席謝偉銓指，不應因個別警員違規，削減整個部門的撥款。他擔心會令所有警署下月被逼停止運作，屆時受影響的只會是市民。他又指，只有罪犯及想推翻政權的人，才會希望警隊停止運作。經民聯盧偉國則指，削減特首辦的開支令人不能認同，形容特首是香港首長，如削減其開支等同令香港中樞系統停擺，又形容反對派議員用盡方法拖垮本港年輕人的未來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/03/20200318_PO_%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E5%8F%8A%E5%B0%B9%E5%85%86%E5%A0%85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F03%2F20200318_PO_%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25B0%25B9%25E5%2585%2586%25E5%25A0%2585.jpg&h=fd65eb42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄺俊宇（左）尹兆堅（右）。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n民主黨鄺俊宇表示，特首林鄭月娥在抗疫工作上不在狀態，令市民在疫情初期要在寒冬下排隊買口罩，支持削減特首辦開支。尹兆堅指，提出修訂除了是抗議行為，亦為阻止政府透過臨時撥款暗渡陳倉予警隊購買水炮車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/12/191209_CR_%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE2_fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F12%2F191209_CR_%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE2_fb.jpg&h=f914d352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄺俊宇 (資料圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/03/20200310_CR_%E5%B0%B9%E5%85%86%E5%A0%85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F03%2F20200310_CR_%25E5%25B0%25B9%25E5%2585%2586%25E5%25A0%2585.jpg&h=a0a846d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尹兆堅。 資料圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6120148-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8A%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6%E5%8F%8A%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%98%8E%E7%BA%8C%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0?current_cat=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F6120148-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2589%258A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%3Fcurrent_cat%3D1&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzM22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=f71f4b9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6120148-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8A%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6%E5%8F%8A%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%98%8E%E7%BA%8C%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0?current_cat=1</a>"},{"pid":"a04b3009a3d766e3fbdf2c8f08cebd9e425a8568","tid":1932128,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"美國戰線著曬火ar ar ar！ChinaliedPeopleDied！入嚟幫拖！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932116</a>"},{"pid":"aca555d094e3664621bb5801ec1db5276bf7bb7c","tid":1932128,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"【媒體懶人堂】三招對抗藍絲文宣戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan